channel.title: How to change Home Tele in Mage Book
channel.description: Helloooo, i was woundering how to change it so when you click on the home tele in the mage book, you can change were you spawn. Ive look for the X and Y axis spots, but every time you click on it, it teleports you somewhere close by the real X and Y axis. Can someone help me find how to change it? Im using Delta Base if that matters. Thanks.

item.title: How to change Home Tele in Mage Book
item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

ClickingMost, find
case 50235:
On the original deltascape its

c.triggerTele(2999+misc.random(3), 3377+misc.random(3), 0);

Just change it to

c.triggerTele([b]A[/b], [b]B[/b], [b]C[/b]);
[b]A[/b] - New home X Coord [b]B[/b] - New home Y Coord [b]C[/b] - New height

Read full topic
